properties.Name: CustomerFinancialProfile
properties.Description: A profile of financial information or characteristics describing the Customer as of the associated date.

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: Date
Columns.Description: The date for the which the Financial Profile information is compiled, recorded or effective as-of.

Columns.Name: EstimatedAnnualIncome
Columns.Description: The Customer's estimated gross annual income.

Columns.Name: EstimatedAnnualSalaryIncome
Columns.Description: The amount of annual income that is attributable to salary income.

Columns.Name: EstimatedAnnualInvestmentsIncome
Columns.Description: The amount of annual income that is attributable to investments.

Columns.Name: EstimatedLiquidSecuritiesNetWorth
Columns.Description: The amount of customer net worth that is held in liquid securities that can be readily liquidated or turned into cash.

Columns.Name: EstimatedCashNetWorth
Columns.Description: The amount of Customer net worth that is either in cash or near cash equivalents.

Columns.Name: EstimatedPersonalPropertyNetWorth
Columns.Description: The amount of net worth that is in personal real estate holdings.

Columns.Name: EstimatedRealEstateLoansAmount
Columns.Description: The estimated real estate loans held by the customer as of the associate timestamp.

Columns.Name: EstimatedInvestmentPropertyNetWorth
Columns.Description: The amount of net worth that is in investment (non-personal) real estate holdings.

Columns.Name: EstimatedCurrentSecuritiesPortfolioValue
Columns.Description: The estimated value of the Customer's current equities and bond portfolio.

Columns.Name: LiquidAssetsAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of liquid assets ('near money') such as time deposits, treasury bills, and other short-term securities that can readily be turned into cash on short notice.

Columns.Name: RealEstateAssetsAmount
Columns.Description: The real estate assets held by the customer during the period.

Columns.Name: FederalTaxBracketPercentage
Columns.Description: The estimated US federal tax bracket that the customer is in during the period.
